comments: Dr. Sumpter is truly a very thorough and helpful professor. I have him on Tuesday\'s and Thursday\'s but his lectures are rarely over an hour in length. He gives you the exact information you will need for your tests along with bringing in historical artifacts that pertain to the lecture that day. He does like class discussion, so speak up.
